						<div class="postbody">Heh, now you get to learn the most obscure instructions that test the overflow flag: BVC and BVS. Overflow is the true signed equivalent to the carry flag. Er and you must use ADC or SBC, since only they set/clear the overflow flag based on the result.</div>

